               <item n="m_translation_old">a1 The &lt;i&gt;saṃgha&lt;/i&gt; of ?-&lt;i&gt;ṣkuneke&lt;/i&gt; addresses his greetings to &lt;i&gt;Nāri&lt;/i&gt; the General: Oh lord! (As) you know it fully (by your)-self, the monastery of (your) own father does (now) belong to you. ... ///
